<br /><strong>6  - 伦敦芬斯伯里公园</strong></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slayer-reunite-and-announce-first-live-shows-in-five-years-3590923">去年秋天，斯莱耶（Slayer）参加了五年来的第一场演出</a>，当时他们参加了两个美国节日：芝加哥暴动节和余震。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slayer-announce-final-dates-of-farewell-tour-2526467">在告别之旅的“最终竞选”之后，他们于2019年退休</a>。</p><p>最近，该乐队于7月份宣布在魁北克节（D&#39;étédeQuébec）举行，这是他们六年来的第一届加拿大演出 - 以及今年9月在肯塔基州路易斯维尔的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bring-me-the-horizon-sleep-token-deftones-lead-150-names-on-stacked-louder-than-life-festival-2025-line-up-3841667">Life 2025年的大声浪费</a>。之后，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slayer-appear-to-tease-2025-uk-reunion-shows-3842282">开始提示他们要越过池塘。</a></p><p>他们对英国的访问也来了，因为他们今年夏天还计划了另一场演出 - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-final-show-birmingham-july-2025-metalla-slayer-pantera-line-up-tickets-3835042">参加了7月5日在伯明翰阿斯顿的Villa Park举行的Black Sabbath举行的巨大的最终音乐会</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3763410" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3763410" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3763410" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Slayer-performing.jpg" alt="Slayer的Kerry King在2019年6月16日在Donington Park下载节上现场表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Slayer-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Slayer-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Slayer-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Slayer-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Slayer-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Slayer-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3763410" class="wp-caption-text"> Slayer的Kerry King在2019年6月16日在Donington Park下载节上现场表演。</figcaption></figure><p>尽管乐队最后一次在2019年的下载节上在英国演出，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slayers-last-ever-tour-end-2019-2371351">但他们在池塘这一侧的最终巡回演出日期是前一年的</a>，并在伦敦的温布利竞技场停了下来。</p><p> Slayer一直在庆祝四十年的另一种方式是为名为Slaytanic诗句的粉丝推出虚拟博物馆。这包括罕见的纪念品，独家见解，无数故事等等，可以<a href="https://www.slayer.net/pages/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查看。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slayer-announce-first-uk-dates-in-six-years-buy-tickets-3843375">Slayer后宣布六年来英国的第一个约会 - 包括巨大的伦敦演出，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
新米莉·鲍比·布朗大片正在获得视频游戏前传https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/electric-state-video-game-netflix-netflix-millie-bobby-brown-brown-3843370?utm_source = rss＆source = rss＆utm_medium = rsss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = electric-state-bbrecn--bame-n-n-n-n-netnet-n-netnet-netAli Shutler Tue, 04 Mar 2025 10:27:12 +0000 Film NewsGaming NewsNewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3843370 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Millie Bobby Brown，Chris Pratt和Ke Huy Quan在“电力状态”中。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “电力状态”即将在本月晚些时候将于Netflix</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/electric-state-video-game-netflix-millie-bobby-brown-3843370">New Millie Bobby Brown Blockbuster发表的帖子正在获得视频游戏的前传</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Millie Bobby Brown，Chris Pratt和Ke Huy Quan在“电力状态”中。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Electric-State-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/millie-bobby-brown">Millie Bobby Brown</a> &#39;s upcoming <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a> film <em>The Electric State</em> is getting a video game prequel.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE:</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/russo-brothers-joe-anthony-absolute-scenes-marvel-netflix-3284403"><strong>Joe and Anthony Russo on their most iconic film scenes: “Chris Evans&#39; ass is America&#39;s ass”</strong></a></li></ul><p> <em>The Electric State</em> is “set in the aftermath of a robot uprising in an alternate version of the &#39;90s” and “follows an orphaned teenager who ventures across the American West with a cartoon-inspired robot, a smuggler, and his sidekick in search of her younger brother.” Brown will play the orphaned Michelle, with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-pratt">Chris Pratt</a> , Giancarlo Esposito and Ke Huy Quan also set to star in the film. Anthony Mackie, Woody Harrelson and Brian Cox will voice various robots.</p><p> Directed by The Russo Brothers ( <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/avengers-endgame-review-2479864">Avengers: Endgame</a></em> ), <em>The Electric State</em> will be available to stream on Netflix from March 14.</p><p> Netflix has also confirmed a video game prequel will be released shortly afterwards. <em>The Electric State: Kid Cosmo</em> is a “bite-sized adventure puzzle game” that will be available on mobile from March 18 for all Netflix subscribers. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Electric State: Kid Cosmo | Official Game Trailer | Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YwcVqSwtSMs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “Kid Cosmo needs your help! Blast through an &#39;80s-inspired puzzle adventure game-within-a-game alongside boy wonder Chris and his big sister Michelle as they navigate coming of age in the retro-futuristic world of <em>The Electric State</em> ,” reads the <a href="https://about.netflix.com/en/news/the-electric-state-kid-cosmo-prequel-game-coming-to-netflix-march-18" target="_blank" rel="noopener">official description</a> . “This narrative-driven game takes place before the events of the movie and spans five years, blending gameplay with emotional storytelling to create an immersive experience.”</p><p> The Russo Brothers helped develop <em>The Electric State: Kid Cosmo</em> through their media company AGBO. “We want to tell new stories,” Joe Russo told <a href="https://variety.com/2025/gaming/news/the-electric-state-video-game-prequel-netflix-russos-1236325355/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Variety</a> . “We want to tell new stories with new characters and new worlds that people haven&#39;t seen before. We have three that we&#39;re currently working on [and] the intention is for every world we build to have the scale and depth of a Star Wars universe, but in a different genre. And then we&#39;ll build materials around those new worlds. We&#39;ll tell stories in different ways using different media in those worlds.” However he also revealed he “would definitely be open” to making an Avengers video game.</p><p> Netflix previously <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/squid-game-unleashed-will-be-free-to-play-for-limited-time-3822514">released a video game tie-in</a> to celebrate the launch of <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/squid-game">Squid Game</a></em> season two. The streamer currently has a library of more than 120 games that are available at no extra charge to Netflix subscribers however in 2022, it was reported that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/less-than-1-per-cent-of-netflixs-221million-subscribers-play-its-games-3285997">less than 1 per cent of Netflix&#39;s 221million subscribers actually play the games</a> on offer.</p><p> In other news, Millie Bobby Brown has <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/millie-bobby-brown-slams-tabloids-criticising-her-appearance-i-refuse-to-apologise-for-growing-up-3843306">slammed numerous articles that have criticised her appearance</a> . “I refuse to apologise for growing up. I refuse to make myself smaller to fit the unrealistic expectations of people who can&#39;t handle seeing a girl become a woman,” she said. “I will not be shamed for how I look, how I dress, or how I present myself.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/electric-state-video-game-netflix-millie-bobby-brown-3843370">New Millie Bobby Brown blockbuster is getting a video game prequel</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
